She heard the message come over on Prowl's commlink.
She looked at Prowl. She knew that if she faught again, she would 
more that likely get killed.  She barely made it through the last 
fight. She found a little confidence in herself this time though.
"Oh man, and I just dinner too. Leave it to a Pred to ruin a nice 
meal. Oh well, I'll follow you to the base and cover your back."
